Item 4.01. Changes in Registrant's Certifying Accountant
        On September 30, 2004, the Audit Committee of the Board of Directors of Balchem Corporation ("Balchem") engaged McGladrey & Pullen LLP ("McGladrey & Pullen") as Balchem's new Independent Registered Public Accounting Firm for the fiscal year ending December 31, 2004. The engagement was effective immediately.
        During Balchem's two most recent fiscal years and the period from the end of the most recent fiscal year to the date of engagement of McGladrey & Pullen, neither Balchem nor anyone acting on its behalf consulted with McGladrey & Pullen with respect to the application of accounting principles to a specified transaction, either completed or proposed, or the type of audit opinion that might be rendered on Balchem's financial statements, or any other matters or events set forth in Items 304(a)(2)(i) and (ii) of Regulation S-K.
