nd Assumption Agreement" means the Assignment and Assumption ------------------------------------ Agreement executed in connection herewith. "Bill of Sale" means the Bill of Sale executed in connection herewith. ------------ "Business Day" means any day other than Saturday, Sunday and any day which ------------ is a legal holiday under the laws of the State of Illinois or a day on which banking institutions in such state are authorized by law or other governmental action to close.
