allments commencing on the tenth (10th) day of such seventh (7th) month. 4. Except as expressly amended by the terms of this Amendment, all other terms and conditions of the Agreement remain unchanged and in full force and effect. IN WITNESS WHEREOF, the Parties have executed this Amendment as of the date first written above. BALCHEM CORPORATION DINO A. ROSSI By: /s/ John Y. Televantos /s/ Dino A. Rossi ------------------------------ ----------------------------------- (Signature) (Signature) John Y. Televantos Dino A. Rossi - ---------------------------------- ------------------------------------ (Print name) (Print name) Title: Director Title: President & CEO --------------------------- ---------------------------- Date: 12/9/05 Date: 12/9/05 --------------------------- ----------------------------


