any claim of immunity on behalf of the Company or any other obligor or with respect to any Property of the Company or any other obligor;
(D)
  
   
the waiver, compromise, settlement, release or termination of any or all of the obligations, covenants or agreements of (1) the Company under the Notes or any of the other Financing Documents, (2) a co-guarantor of the Notes;
